你能够调用以下的API:
[['CryptoResearch.get_research_report', {'name': 'CryptoResearch.get_research_report', 'description': 'get the most recent research reports relating to a specific topic in cryptocurrency investment', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'topic', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The topic of the research report'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'results', 'description': 'A list of research reports including title, summary, and author'}]}], ['CryptoEducation.get_success_cases', {'name': 'CryptoEducation.get_success_cases', 'description': 'This function retrieves the details of successful cryptocurrency investment cases given the type of education.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'educationType', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The type of education used in the investment cases.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'cases', 'description': 'A list of successful cases including investor name, education details, and investment outcome'}]}], ['CryptoTools.get_investment_tools', {'name': 'CryptoTools.get_investment_tools', 'description': 'This function retrieves a list of practical tools for cryptocurrency investment.', 'required_parameters': [], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'tools', 'description': 'A list of investment tools including tool name, description, and usage'}]}], ['CryptoAdvisor.get_investment_advice', {'name': 'CryptoAdvisor.get_investment_advice', 'description': 'This function provides investment advice based on research reports, success cases, and available tools.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'researchReport', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The research report used for advice.'}, {'name': 'successCases', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The success cases used for advice.'}, {'name': 'tools', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The tools used for advice.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'advice', 'description': 'A list of investment advice including strategy, risk management, and recommended tools'}]}]]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `api1` 并传入 `arg1` 和 `arg2`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "api1",
    "args": "{'arg1': 'value1', 'arg2': 'value2', ...}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。

